snippet.title: The Deadly Path - Release Date Trailer | FGS LIVE FROM GDC
snippet.description:
A new trailer announcing the release date of The Deadly Path, a unique building management and roguelike strategy game. This moreish tactical experience is coming to PC as a digital exclusive on March 25th.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #thedeadlypath #gdc 

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
